# trivy`). Prettier reflows them, so every check.sh run dirties the last
# release's committed reports — and the next release rewrites them unformatted
# again. They are machine output; leave them exactly as Trivy emits them.
security

# nginx include: Prettier infers an `.inc` file as HTML and reflows it, which
# collapses the line-based `#` comments and directives into invalid config
